Package: colSBM
Title: Stochastic Block Model for Collection of Networks
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Saint-Clair", "Chabert-Liddell", , "academic@chabert-liddell.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5604-7308")),
    person("Louis", "Lacoste", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Finds a common mesoscale structure in a collection of
    networks by using a Stochastic Block Model (SBM) extension for the
    joint modeling of collection of networks as described in
    <arXiv:2206.00560>.  Provides a clustering of the nodes of each
    networks.  Classifies networks in sub-collections of networks with
    similar mesoscale structures.
